ðŸ”¹ Database Setup:
1. Run in MySQL Workbench:
   CREATE DATABASE studentdb;

   CREATE TABLE students (
       id INT PRIMARY KEY AUTO_INCREMENT,
       name VARCHAR(100),
       age INT,
       email VARCHAR(100),
       course VARCHAR(100)
   );

2. Update DB credentials in resources/config.properties.

ðŸ”¹ Run Instructions:
